    "details": "Jesse Smith (upstream author of the doas program) reported:\n\n> Previous versions of \\\"doas\\\" transferred most environment variables,\n> such as USER, HOME, and PATH from the original user to the target\n> user. Passing these variables could cause files in the wrong path or\n> home directory to be read (or written to), which resulted in potential\n> security problems.\n>\n> Many thanks to Sander Bos for reporting this issue and explaining how\n> it can be exploited.\n",
